## Mandatory Notice

{{ project.disclaimer }}

This guide is **PRELIMINARY**, **not for construction**, and is not a replacement for professional supervision, permits, inspections, licensed architects, licensed engineers, licensed electricians, licensed mechanical/plumbing professionals, fire-safety reviewers, or local authorities.

